{
  "stem": "11179.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what they did actually-- they cut from the bottom of the shirt off, then the tail, and made collars.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had learned how to make custom shirts, actually, in Germany, but in a very rushed, short way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so-- so they did a little bit, did a little bit of-- made a little bit of money that-- that way for a while.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And later on, my father started to-- actually worked in a kitchen later on doing any kind of work in the-- in the kitchen of the-- where they had [INAUDIBLE] potatoes and cooking and so on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was-- it was-- my father never got over-- he didn't get as bad or [INAUDIBLE] some other people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But really, he did never get over that he was once thrown out of what he loved to do, and that was selling.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Selling-- not door-to-door type selling-- selling companies, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was not a salesman like the kind of sell-- maybe even insurance policies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- his was on-- on a different level.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the people he talked to were-- were public relations officers of large companies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Frankfurt, they sent him to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Berlin was mostly the headquarters of the big companies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's when we moved-- why we moved to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he did very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think he did probably 80% to 90% of the business that paper got was through him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he went to-- to-- to-- to these trade fairs, you know, and-- and-- and expositions and so on-- shows, radio shows, and so on-- and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For them, in the different places like Leipzig, Frankfurt, and Berlin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Shanghai?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must say, a lot of people were very positive.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
